Package org.hyperledger.fabric.gateway

Interface X509Identity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Identity
    public interface X509Identity
extends Identity
    Identity comprising an X.509 certificate and associated private key. Instances are created using Identities.newX509Identity(String, X509Certificate, PrivateKey).
